<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>GNU Test Coverage</title>
  <style>
:root {
  color-scheme: dark;
  --bg: #0a1020;
  --bg-alt: #0e1730;
  --panel: rgba(14, 23, 48, 0.86);
  --line: rgba(187, 197, 219, 0.16);
  --ink: #e8ebf6;
  --muted: #b7bfd9;
  --good: #47c271;
  --warn: #d8ca86;
  --bad: #ff4b5c;
  --accent: #9cc2ff;
  --track: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; }
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
  color: var(--ink);
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(47, 86, 167, 0.18), transparent 34%),
    radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(39, 120, 92, 0.16), transparent 28%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, #09101f 0%, #0a1121 46%, #08101d 100%);
}
main {
  max-width: 1180px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 48px 24px 72px;
}
h1, h2 { margin: 0; }
p { margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }
a { color: var(--accent); }
code, .mono {
  font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", "SFMono-Regular", monospace;
}
.lede {
  margin-top: 16px;
  max-width: 840px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}
.meta {
  margin-top: 14px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.95rem;
}
.summary {
  margin-top: 28px;
  display: grid;
  gap: 14px;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
}
.summary-card {
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 18px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
  padding: 18px 18px 16px;
}
.summary-label {
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.84rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.summary-value {
  margin-top: 6px;
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.summary-detail {
  margin-top: 8px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.94rem;
}
.panel {
  margin-top: 30px;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 22px;
  background: var(--panel);
  box-shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
  padding: 24px 22px 20px;
}
.section-copy {
  margin-top: 12px;
  color: var(--muted);
  max-width: 840px;
}
.details-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 22px;
}
details.group {
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 18px;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
}
details.group summary {
  list-style: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 16px 18px;
}
details.group summary::-webkit-details-marker {
  display: none;
}
.summary-row {
  display: grid;
  gap: 14px;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(110px, 160px) minmax(120px, 160px) 1fr minmax(120px, 180px);
  align-items: center;
}
.counts {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}
.row-note {
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.93rem;
  text-align: right;
}
.progress {
  display: flex;
  width: 100%;
  height: 18px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--track);
}
.progress-segment {
  display: block;
  height: 100%;
}
.progress-segment.good { background: var(--good); }
.progress-segment.oos { background: rgba(183, 191, 217, 0.36); }
.progress-segment.warn { background: var(--warn); }
.progress-segment.bad { background: var(--bad); }
.group-body {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  padding: 10px 18px 16px;
}
.subtable {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
}
.subtable th, .subtable td {
  padding: 10px 8px;
  text-align: left;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  vertical-align: top;
}
.subtable th {
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
}
.subtable tr:last-child td {
  border-bottom: 0;
}
.pill {
  display: inline-block;
  min-width: 76px;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.84rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-align: center;
}
.good { color: var(--good); background: rgba(71, 194, 113, 0.14); }
.oos { color: #d6dceb; background: rgba(183, 191, 217, 0.18); }
.warn { color: var(--warn); background: rgba(216, 202, 134, 0.14); }
.bad { color: var(--bad); background: rgba(255, 75, 92, 0.14); }
.na { color: var(--muted); background: rgba(183, 191, 217, 0.14); }
.test-note {
  margin-top: 4px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.88rem;
}
@media (max-width: 920px) {
  .summary-row {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .row-note {
    text-align: left;
  }
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <h1>GNU Test Coverage</h1>
    <p class="lede"><code>gbash</code> is tested against the GNU coreutils test suite. The results below are grouped by the upstream GNU test categories, matching the structure of the suite rather than a derived per-command attribution layer.</p>
    <p class="meta">Generated <strong>{{ .Summary.GeneratedAt }}</strong> against GNU coreutils <strong>{{ .Summary.GNUVersion }}</strong>. Raw data: <a href="summary.json">summary.json</a>.</p>

    <section class="summary">
      <article class="summary-card">
        <div class="summary-label">In-Scope Test Pass</div>
        <div class="summary-value">{{ formatPercent .InScopePassPct }}</div>
        <div class="summary-detail">{{ .SelectedDetail }}</div>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <div class="summary-label">Runnable Test Pass</div>
        <div class="summary-value">{{ formatPercent .Summary.Suite.PassPctRunnable }}</div>
        <div class="summary-detail">{{ .RunnableDetail }}</div>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <div class="summary-label">Coverage Categories</div>
        <div class="summary-value">{{ len .Summary.Categories }}</div>
        <div class="summary-detail">{{ .Summary.Suite.SelectedTotal }} total tests across upstream GNU categories.</div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <h2>Coverage per category</h2>
      <p class="section-copy">Click categories to see the names of the tests. Green indicates a passing test, yellow indicates a skipped test, grey indicates an out-of-scope test excluded from the overall pass rate, and red indicates a failed, errored, or unreported test.</p>

      <div class="details-list">
        {{- range .Summary.Categories }}
        <details class="group">
          <summary>
            <div class="summary-row">
              <strong class="mono">{{ .Name }}</strong>
              <span class="mono counts">{{ .Counts }}</span>
              <div class="progress" aria-hidden="true">
                {{- range .Segments }}
                <span class="progress-segment {{ .Class }}" style="width: {{ .Width }}"></span>
                {{- end }}
              </div>
              <span class="row-note">{{ .RowNote }}</span>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="group-body">
            <table class="subtable">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>Test</th>
                  <th>Status</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                {{- range .Tests }}
                <tr>
                  <td class="mono">{{ .Path }}{{ if .Filtered }}<div class="test-note">{{ .FilterReason }}</div>{{ end }}</td>
                  <td><span class="pill {{ testStatusClass .Status .Filtered }}">{{ if .Filtered }}out of scope{{ else }}{{ .Status }}{{ end }}</span></td>
                </tr>
                {{- end }}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </details>
        {{- end }}
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
